# Console-based Pet Adoption Platform

## Project Overview
This is a console-based application that allows users to adopt pets. The platform supports viewing available pets, adopting pets, and basic data validation. The application uses a simple text-based interface to interact with the user.

## Features
- **View Available Pets**: Lists pets that are available for adoption.
- **Adopt a Pet**: Allows users to adopt a pet by entering its name.
- **User Registration**: Users can register to track which pets they have adopted.
- **Pet Search**: Allows users to search for pets by type or name.

## Installation Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/pet-adoption-platform.git
javac PetAdoptionApp.java
java PetAdoptionApp
1. View Available Pets
2. Adopt a Pet
3. Exit
Please choose an option: 1
Enter the name of the pet you want to adopt: Buddy
Successfully adopted Buddy!

